om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> ho=
lding a hearing</a> on =E2=80=9CRecent Bank Failures and the Federal Regula=
tory Response.=E2=80=9D Here are the prepared testimonies of <a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30986595.262435/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
YmFua2luZy5zZW5hdGUuZ292L2ltby9tZWRpYS9kb2MvQmFyciUyMFRlc3RpbW9ueSUyMDMtMjg=
tMjMxLnBkZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB68bca0d3" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" items=
cope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorati=
on: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000=
; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Michael Barr</a>, t=
he vice chair for supervision at the Federal Reserve, <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30986595.262435/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZmRpYy5=
nb3YvbmV3cy9zcGVlY2hlcy8yMDIzL3NwbWFyMjcyMy5wZGY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd=
ed6b4a7" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" s=
