 the US Treasury.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Gruenberg=E2=80=99s testimony helps clear up o=
ne small mystery of the recent bank failures: What <a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30986595.262435/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZX=
JnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMTMvc3ZiLWNvdWxkbi10LWlnbm9yZS1pd=
